commentary: Cummins to Hendricks, 2 runs, OUT he's been run out coming back for a third! What an error from South Africa. Length delivery, clipped off the pads through midwicket, it was a comfortable two and they pushed for the third. Markram didn't seem to be putting in the hard yards, then brought out the dive but it couldn't save him. Bat may just have been over the line, but it had never been grounded in the process. Something from nothing for Australia. Stoinis was the chaser, terrific take at the stumps by Carey
